metadata.name: A.S.Jesus
metadata.description:
I have a friend, and his name is Artem. He looks like Jesus. 
At this moment, he is fighting for our country in the Ukrainian army against the russian invaders. He dreams of going to Burning Man, and I believe we can go there together after the victory of Ukraine. 

After selling this art, I will buy and give him a ticket to Burning Man. 
And a part of the amount will be donated to the Burning Man Project. 

Collection: Ukrainians at Burning Man
Format: 2048x1152, png
Edition 1 of 1
